  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Sofosbuvir plus daclatasvir with or without ribavirin is one of the currently recommended
      treatment option for chronic hepatitis C. The objectives were to identify factors associated
      with sofosbuvir/daclatasvir plasma concentrations variations and to evaluate their impact on
      viral kinetics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
